<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header', { active: 'home' }) %>
<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Toss</h1>
    <p>A money-free community exchange. List something, borrow something. Items keep circulating.</p>
    <p>Built for students and newcomers who need tools temporarily—without buying things they can't keep.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/post" class="btn-primary">Post an item →</a>
      <a href="/browse" class="btn-secondary">Browse what's available</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="rules">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon"></div>
      <div>
        <h2>List first, then borrow</h2>
        <p>You can't receive anything until you've put something up. After you post, you get access to everything on the platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon"></div>
      <div>
        <h2>One exchange per week</h2>
        <p>Exchanges happen once a week. Keeps things fair and items moving.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
      <div class="icon"></div>
      <div>
        <h2>6-month commitment & card on file</h2>
        <p>Minimum 6-month commitment from your first listing—builds trust and cuts down on one-off buys. We keep a card on file; if someone doesn't return an item, they're charged. So the community stays reliable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <p class="footer-note">New to the city? Moving often? Need a sander, a drill, or a pot for a few months? Toss lets you use what you need and pass it on.</p>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
